# Quiz Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create quiz (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/quizzes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "NestJS Basics Quiz",
  "moduleId": "<module-id>",
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "questions": [
    {
      "content": "What is NestJS?",
      "options": ["A framework", "A database", "A language"],
      "correctOptionIndex": 0
    }
  ]
}

### Get all quizzes (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/quizzes
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get quiz by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/quizzes/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update quiz (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/quizzes/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

### Submit quiz implementation (protected, current user intern)
POST http://localhost:3001/quizzes/{{id}}/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "answers": [0, 1, 0]
}
